(7, 1, 'Su Pan 2 readies for generating power', '\r\n                                         \r\n                                      <span class="noidungtomtat"><p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><font color="#666666">In about 70<span>&nbsp; </span>small\r\n and medium hydropower projects in Lao Cai, Su Pan 2 hydropower project \r\nby Song Da- Hoang Lien Hydropower joint-stock Company (Song Da \r\nCorporation) as an investor. <span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><font color="#666666">Su Pan 2 Hydroelectric Plant (with design\r\n capacity of 34.5 MW 3 units) located Ngoi Bo, Ban Ho commune, \r\n<st1:place w:st="on">\r\n<st1:city w:st="on">Sa</st1:city>\r\n<st1:state w:st="on">Pa</st1:state></st1:place> district, Lao Cai \r\nprovince.</font></span></font></span></p></span>', 'gryrgdfgr.png', '<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="90%"><tbody><tr><td><table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"><div align="left"><span class="noidungtomtat"><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><font color="#666666">&nbsp;Starting construction<span>&nbsp;\r\n </span>in<span>&nbsp; </span>the early year of 2007, in 2008 the work has \r\nspent a<span>&nbsp; </span>the most heavy rainy season. By<span>&nbsp; </span>both\r\n constructing and having to confront the severe weather, in March this \r\nyear, the \r\n<st1:place w:st="on">Song Da</st1:place> - Hoang Lien Hydropower Company\r\n has conducted phase 1 of<span>&nbsp; </span>Muong Hoa stream. Up to then, \r\nnearly two thirds of basic construction volume of work \r\ncompleted.Including the left side foundation holes of the<span>&nbsp; </span>rising\r\n dam, the foundation hole of<span>&nbsp; </span>the spillway, the phase 1 \r\ninfrastructure plant infrastructure. The drain, the wall upstream 