ench digging by Song Da 10 Company- a combative tunnel \r\ndigging unit tunnel undertook, so there is nothing to<span>&nbsp; </span>be \r\nafraid-worthy. The praiseworthy thing is that devices for the factory \r\ncarried to the construction site. From one quarter in 2010, begin \r\ninstalling equipments for the machine team for generating power in \r\nJune,2010. <br>\r\n<br>Along with executing Su Pan 2 Hydropower, Song Da - Hoang Lien \r\nHydropower joint-stock Company<span>&nbsp; </span>also conducted in \r\npreparation for building Nam Cun Hydropower (40 MW capacity). Executing \r\nRoad from Su Pan 2 to Nam Cun<span>&nbsp; </span>has been 3/9 km. The dam \r\nshoulder construction as also being implemented. <br>\r\n<br>In accordance with its name, the\r\n<st1:place w:st="on">Song Da</st1:place> - Hoang Lien Company want to \r\nstick â€œits tradename with an angle of Hoang Lien Son for the development\r\n of local socio-economic.\r\n<o:p></o:p></font></span></p></span>		  \r\n                       	</div></td></tr>\r\n                      \r\n                  </tbody></table>\r\n           </td></tr><tr>\r\n           </tr><tr><td colspan="2" height="10"><br></td></tr>\r\n	       <tr><td colspan="2" align="right" height="5" width="100%"><span class="tindadang"></span><br></td></tr></tbody></table>', 'CTN Viet Nam', '16/06/2010', 1, 1, 0),
(8, 3, ' Allow vehicles on the widest bridge in Vietnam', '<span class="noidungtomtat"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #CCFFFF; font-family: Tahoma;"><font color="#666666">According to the\r\n plan of Hanoi Peopleâ€™s Committee, on the nex Sep,26<sup>th </sup>, Vinh\r\n Tuy bridge - the widest bridge inVietnam will officially allow \r\nvehicles. Vinh Tuy bridge crosses over the Red River with 5.8 km length \r\nincluding the length crossing river of 3.7 km, bridge surface with<span>&nbsp;\r\n </span>19m width (phase 1).</font></span></span>', 'fewrtevinh.png', '<span class="noidungtomtat"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #CCFFFF; font-family: Tahoma;"><font color="#666666">Total investment\r\n capital of the project is 3598 billion dong, of which, the building \r\npart is 1830 billion dong, the rest is the cost of clearance and \r\nprovision ... The project has moved 1568 households and 13 agencies in \r\nthe area of<span>&nbsp; </span>2 districts Long Bien and Hai Ba Trung in past\r\n four years. The project will complete in June 2010. <br>\r\n<br>Phase 1, to save costs, \r\n<st1:city w:st="on">\r\n<st1:place w:st="on">Hanoi</st1:place></st1:city> city carried out to \r\nbuild bridge surface with 19m width, but the roads linking the bridge \r\nwith 38m width. Phase 2 in the future will continue to expand bridge \r\nsurface as planned. <br>\r\n<br>According to experts on traffic, Vinh Tuy bridge is<span>&nbsp; </span>efficient\r\n\r\n support for the Chuong Duong bridge. This is the inner city bridge, \r\nlinking the Vinh Tuy ward (Hai Ba Trung) to Phuc Dong ward (Long Bien \r\ndistrict). <br>\r\n<br>As planned, the vehicle traffic on the area of<span>&nbsp; </span>Long \r\nBien district and the north of Vinh Tuy bridge will be made as follows: <br>\r\n<br>For vehicles with loading capacity under 10 tons, motorcycles, \r\nmotorbikes can follow the right of Red dyke and Thach Ban route, head \r\nroute in the industry Hanel industrial zone is connected to the routes \r\nof the Vinh Tuy bridge project to go over the bridge to Minh Khai. The \r\nvehicles when going on the<span>&nbsp; </span>right head of Red dyke, Thach \r\nBan road into the project of Vinh Tuy bridge will not turn on traffic \r\nhead in an Hanel industrial zone and vice versa. <br>\r\n<br>Means with loading capacity<span>&nbsp; </span>over 10 tons must go to \r\nNguyen Van Linh street, then go to the main axis in the Hanel industrial\r\n zone<span>&nbsp; </span>connecting to the project to go through the Minh \r\nKhai and they will not be allowed to return to the Thach Ban route. <br>\r\n<br>The transportation from the Long Bien crossing over bridge, entering\r\n the inner city can turn down Nguyen Khoai dyke or go straight to\r\n<st1:street w:st="on">\r\n<st1:address w:st="on">Nguyen Minh Khai street</st1:address></st1:street>\r\n to go into the inner city. The means to go down the south have to go \r\nstraight to\r\n<st1:street w:st="on">\r\n<st1:address w:st="on">Minh Khai street</st1:address></st1:street> to \r\nturn down\r\n<st1:street w:st="on">\r\n<st1:address w:st="on">Tam Chinh street</st1:address></st1:street>. \r\nParticularly, for the vehicles turn on the\r\n<st1:place w:st="on">\r\n<st1:placename w:st="on">Chuong</st1:placename>\r\n<st1:placename w:st="on">Duong</st1:placename>\r\n<st1:placetype w:st="on">Bridge</st1:placetype></st1:place> will turn \r\ndown\r\n<st1:street w:st="on">\r\n<st1:address w:st="on">CV1C street</st1:address></st1:street>. <br>\r\n<br>The vehicles on streets of Hai Ba Trung district and the south of \r\nVinh Tuy bridge to go to area of Long Bien district and the north, \r\nspecifically as follows: The inner city transportation or from the south\r\n can go on Minh Khai routes to pass through Long Bien. For the vehicles \r\nfrom the Thanh Tri<span>&nbsp; </span>can go up bridge by going on the Nguyen\r\n Khoai dyke and turn on CV1B branch<span>&nbsp; </span>to go up the bridge. <br>\r\n<br>The vehicles from Chuong Duong bridge towards Vinh Tuy bridge will \r\ngo pass space under the bridge to turn to the CV1A branch to go up the \r\nbridge. After the vehicles were on the bridge, theywill need to go as \r\nthe folowing directions: The truck under 10 tons and primitivety, can \r\nturn on roads in Hanel industrial zone;\r\n<st1:street w:st="on">\r\n<st1:address w:st="on">Thanh Ban street</st1:address></st1:street> amd \r\nRed right dyke to go to many directions . Particularly,the vehicles over\r\n 10 tons are required to go to Hanel routes to turn to Nguyen Van Linh \r\nfor places.\r\n</font></span></span>', 'CTN Viet Nam', '16/06/2010', 1, 1, 0);

